release.title: News from
release.descripcion:
__**New**__
- Levels: Shows the list of roles by server level previously configured.
- AddBlackList: New command that allows disabling commands for channels, categories, roles, users or the entire server.
 - AddWhiteList: You can add channels, categories, roles or users that are not affected by the BlackList of certain commands as well.
- DeleteBlackList and DeleteWhiteList: Commands to remove configuration from the corresponding commands.
- AddExcludeXp: Now you can specify in which channels or categories will not receive experience for writing.
- ResetXp: Now you can restart the experience of a user or the entire server.

__**Changes**__
- Enable and Disable: These commands were removed to be replaced by Ê»AddBlackList` and Ê»AddWhiteList`.
- Rank: Now, if the server experience is activated, it will show said rank instead of global, to see the global in such cases, you will have to put `sl! rank global`.
- Top: The same as the previous command, plus a rewrite of the code improving and the noticeable change will be the handling of pages.
- DeleteRolLevelUp: It was separated from the `delete` command so that it is easy to identify and use it.
- DeleteXp: It was also separated and improved by fixing some errors of assignment of corresponding level with the added xp.
- Config : The sections corresponding to the new have been added.

 __**Fixes** __
- Xp: Fix that did not give the roles correctly.
- AddRolLevelUp: Properties were removed and some aspects were fixed.
- Cookie: Fixed the function of mentioning a user by their id.
- Config: Fixed an occasional error from the last imo embed.
- The appearance of some texts has been improved.
- Bugs: Many small bugs fixed in various commands and events.

 __**Notices**__
Music: The entire music category has been disabled for be fixed in future updates.
release.footer: These are the changes of the version {version} any problem you can enter the support server. | Developed by {dev}.
